[4.919542, "o", "Once you know everyone'\"'\"'s preferences and schedules, pick a restaurant that works for everyone. Don'\"'\"'t forget to factor in commute time from the office to the restaurant. \r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[4.919586, "o", "\u001b[?2004h"]
[4.919616, "o", "> "]
[4.919787, "o", "Make the reservation using your company name. \r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[4.919854, "o", "\u001b[?2004h> "]
